"otherness" of these characters.%0a%3c %0a%3c Discrimination against Indian accents has been seen in various other TV shows including Phineas and Ferb (Baljeet) and Jessie (Ravi Ross). Unfortunately, jokes about accents in media have real-life consequences, and many Indians face mockery due to their accents because the media makes it sound okay to do so.%0a%3c %0a%3c Link to article: https://www.chicagotribune.com/columns/heidi-stevens/ct-heidi-stevens-hank-azaria-apology-for-apu-accent-stigma-0414-20210414-vxrlet3blnftjgxm4zi2ymf7t4-story.html%0a%3c %0a%3c Other links:%0a%3c https://www.latg.org/blog/2018/06/24/indian-english/%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
